# Project Name:

FynCom

## Short (1‚Äì2 sentence) Description:

FynCom creates digital trust by adding crypto into calls, texts, emails & DMs, requiring unknown senders to stake a small refundable deposit before recipients are notified of their contact request. Refunds are automatically issued based on call times or thread responses, but otherwise forfeited to the recipient; This creates a marketplace where highly-contacted people can monetize their responses to unknown senders who value that enough to keep paying.

## Longer Description:

FynCom is redefining the economics of digital trust. Today, spam, scams, and AI-generated fraud thrive because it costs bad actors nothing to reach everyone. FynCom solves this by introducing an economic proof-of-intent protocol where every communication from an unknown sender is required to have a small, refundable stake from the sender. If the recipient accepts the request but doens't engage long enough, the stake is forfeited at an 80:20 rate to the recipient and FynCom's treasury.

For example:

* with phone calls, our defaults are $0.05 to start a call, and a 25 second conversation in order for a refund to be issued; Senders don't lose anything if the call is not connected.  
* With messages (text, emails, DMs), our defaults are $0.01 to start a conversation, and 3 thread responses for a refund. 

Premium members can set their own rates and our next phase will add options to automate these refundable paywall criteria.

Our patented Time-Based Nano-Transaction System (US 11,310,368 B2) powers this mechanism and has already proven effective through KarmaCall, our mobile app that blocks unknown unstaked calls and texts, with the added benefit of "cash-back" for every blocked call or text (which comes out of our own treasury). With over 500,000 "cash-back" transactions over calls, texts, and emails, we‚Äôve demonstrated that economic trust can scale.

Now, we‚Äôre expanding this system into the agentic AI economy, serving as the human's personal "negotiator" where the FynCom agent can automatically handle the negotiation of the stake and refund criteria, ensuring that humans always get the greatest chance at genuine communications or more cash in their wallets. This allows humans to be able to protect themselves from the increasingly massive amounts of inbound communications that will come from the rise of autonomous agents.

FynCom is not just another crypto project, it‚Äôs a new foundation for value-based communication, built to restore trust to legacy communication networks, and create new markets in the world of SMS, Phone, Social DMs, and Emails.
